targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  $__timeGroupAlias("Cases"."date",$__interval), 
  sum("Cases"."dead") AS "Gemeldete Todesfälle pro Tag"
FROM   "Cases" 
WHERE
"countyID" IN (SELECT "id" FROM "Counties" WHERE "state" = 'Schleswig-Holstein')
GROUP BY 1
ORDER BY 1
